8x the company=E2=80=99s 2026 outlook vs. 5.7x at Fox and 5.6x at Warner Br=
os. Discovery), we expect investor enthusiasm to remain tempered,=E2=80=9D =
Guggenheim analyst Michael Morris wrote today. But I think the market is sh=
ort-sighted. As the smallest of the stand-alone legacy studio conglomerates=
