I spoke to Ellison and Gerry Cardinale of RedBird today for a bit. After 15=
 years running Skydance, David still doesn=E2=80=99t seem totally comfortab=
le talking to the media. I=E2=80=99m guessing that growing up the son of an=
 outspoken and conservative tech mogul has instilled in him a healthy disco=
