2. Big cuts in linear: Shell will almost certainly gut the linear TV assets=
 even further. =E2=80=9CThey are very profitable businesses that do need to=
 be managed differently,=E2=80=9D Ellison told me. =E2=80=9CThey need to be=
 managed for cash flow.=E2=80=9D That=E2=80=99s been happening for a while =
