=99t expressly say so, but I got the sense that he=E2=80=99s committed to P=
aramount+ in the U.S., while overseas, he=E2=80=99ll likely pursue the =E2=
=80=9Carms dealer=E2=80=9D strategy and pull back from owned or co-owned st=
reaming platforms. =E2=80=9CIt=E2=80=99s too early to make any definitive d=
eclarations, but you should absolutely evaluate whether or not a licensing =
