=E2=80=9CWhat bothers me about Jeffrey isn=E2=80=99t that he downplayed Joe=
=E2=80=99s condition. He=E2=80=99s the money-raiser=E2=80=A6 his job is to =
stoke excitement to raise money. What=E2=80=99s unforgivable is that Jeffre=
y tried to spin [the president=E2=80=99s] age as his =E2=80=98superpower.=
=E2=80=99 He used that word often, and other words like =E2=80=98asset=E2=
=80=99 and =E2=80=98secret weapon.=E2=80=99 To me, that goes beyond simply =
acknowledging and minimizing what we now know he knew to be a huge problem.=
 He was treating the president like one of his movies=E2=80=94a troubled pr=
oject that loses its star or
director, which must be spun not as a negative but as a positive. =E2=80=98=
Forget what you=E2=80=99ve read and heard, I=E2=80=99ve seen the test score=
s and Biden tested through the roof.=E2=80=99 The problem is we all saw thi=
s movie for ourselves. No amount of marketing and spin can change that.=E2=
=80=9D =E2=80=94An executive

