=E2=80=99s condition. He=E2=80=99s the money-raiser=E2=80=A6 his job is to =
stoke excitement to raise money. What=E2=80=99s unforgivable is that Jeffre=
y tried to spin [the president=E2=80=99s] age as his =E2=80=98superpower.=
