roblem. He was treating the president like one of his movies=E2=80=94a trou=
bled project that loses its star or
director, which must be spun not as a negative but as a <i>positive</i>. =
=E2=80=98Forget what you=E2=80=99ve read and heard, I=E2=80=99ve seen the t=
est scores and Biden tested through the roof.=E2=80=99 The problem is we al=
l saw this movie for ourselves. No amount of marketing and spin can change =
that.=E2=80=9D =E2=80=94<i>An</i> <i>executive</i> <br/></td>
